			<p class="author"><!-- google_ad_section_start(weight=ignore) --><a rel="nofollow" href="./viewtopic.php?p=8862&amp;sid=3debbb39b3de6e0c693e559e427bbcc3#p8862"><img src="./styles/static/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>Post <a href="./viewtopic.php?p=8862&amp;sid=3debbb39b3de6e0c693e559e427bbcc3#p8862" onclick="prompt('Direct link to post:',this.href); return false;"><strong>#10</strong></a>&nbsp;by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=179&amp;sid=3debbb39b3de6e0c693e559e427bbcc3" style="color: #000000;" class="username-coloured">ofahn</a></strong> &raquo; June 3rd, 2012, 4:07 pm <!-- google_ad_section_end --></p>

			

